IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. SumCheck.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01  NUM1    PIC 9(3)    VALUE  7.
01  NUM2    PIC 9(3)    VALUE  4.
01  TOTAL   PIC 9(4)    VALUE  0.
01  STATUS  PIC X(10)   VALUE  SPACES.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    MOVE NUM1 TO TOTAL
    ADD  NUM2 TO TOTAL

    IF TOTAL > 10
        MOVE "TOO LARGE" TO STATUS
    ELSE
        MOVE "OK" TO STATUS
    END-IF

    STOP RUN.
